<h4 id="Article-52839">Safer staffing</h4>
<div id="imageContentd91aed420d984a9f950d8b7dba3d1ae9">
</div>
<p>Our  monthly safer staffing information is published on a dedicated page on Wye Valley NHS Trust's website and in our Public Board Meeting papers .</p>
<p>To access this information <a href="http://www.wyevalley.nhs.uk/about-us/the-trust-board.aspx" title="The Trust Board"></a><a href="http://www.wyevalley.nhs.uk/about-us/our-performance/safer-staffing.aspx">click here</a>.</p>
<p> </p>
<p class="last-updated">Last updated on 10 December 2014.</p>
